            <abstract>
                <p>Commentary of the Apostolic Creed, which is partly a direct translation of each of the Gǝʿǝz words into Amharic and partly a 
                    brief commentary in Amharic introduced in each case with <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘ፡</foreign>. According to 
                    <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/IXFP733G"><seg type="bookSection"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Erho2025Palimpsests"/><title level="a">Ethiopic Palimpsests</title><title level="m">Palimpsests and Related Phenomena across Languages and Cultures</title><title level="s">Studies in Manuscript Cultures</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Ted</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Erho</t:surname></author><editor><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Jost</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Gippert</t:surname></editor><editor><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">José</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Maksimczuk</t:surname></editor><editor><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Hasmik</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Sargsyan</t:surname></editor><pubPlace>Berlin–Boston, MA</pubPlace><publisher>De Gruyter</publisher><date>2025</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Studies in Manuscript Cultures</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">42</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="page">393-431</biblScope><biblScope unit="volume">42</biblScope><note type="url">https://doi.org/10.1515/9783111552170-015</note></bibl> probably from the 17th century.</p>
